<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id76f33cf4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s45d"><num value="45d">§ 45d.</num><heading> Exclusive privileges within park prohibited</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No exclusive privilege shall be granted within said park, or on or over the roads and trails therein, except upon ground leased for the erection of buildings or camps thereon.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id76f33cf5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1926-07-03/ch744/s4">July 3, 1926, ch. 744, § 4</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/44/820">44 Stat. 820</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
